[![Oui: The CLI with a GUI twist](icons/svg/oui-wide.svg)](http://kui.tools)
**Oui** is a tool that enhances the OpenWhisk terminal experience with visualizations. It provides users a modern alternative to ASCII terminals and web-based consoles.
